studyArms.name: PF-04965842 Maintenance
studyArms.description: Subjects who responded to the open-label run-in period are randomized to continue PF-04965842 (200 mg QD).

studyArms.name: Placebo Maintenance
studyArms.description: Subjects who responded to the open-label run-in period are randomized to receive matching placebo.

studyArms.name: Open-Label Run-In
studyArms.description: All subjects receive open-label PF-04965842 200 mg QD for 12 weeks to identify responders.

studyCohorts.name: Responders
studyCohorts.characteristic: Subjects meeting protocol-defined response criteria at Week 12 of the Run-In period.

studyCohorts.name: Non-responders
studyCohorts.characteristic: Subjects not meeting response criteria at Week 12; may roll over to Study B7451015.

epochs.name: Screening
epochs.description: Initial assessment and washout of prohibited AD treatments.

epochs.name: Run-In Induction Treatment Period

epochs.name: Double-Blind Maintenance Treatment Period

epochs.name: Rescue Treatment Period
epochs.description: Open-label rescue treatment for subjects experiencing a flare during the maintenance period.

epochs.name: Follow-up
epochs.description: 4 weeks after the End of Treatment visit.
